len <- 256

# Divide genome into non-overlapping segments of length 256 bases
divide_data <- function (dat){
    limit <- length(dat)
    # limit
    div_data <- c()
    start <- 1
    end <- len
    
    while (end <= limit) {
      if (end%%2560000 == 0){print(end)}
      
      div_data <- append(div_data, c2s(dat[start:end]))
      start <- end + 1
      end <- start + len - 1
    }
      print(length(div_data))
      return(div_data)
}

Count_CG <- function(div_data){
    n_divData <- length(div_data)
    GC_content <- rep(0, n_divData)
    CpG_rate <- rep(0, n_divData)
    
    for (i in 1:n_divData){
        temp_data <- div_data[i]
        nCpG <- str_count(temp_data, 'CG')
        nC <- str_count(temp_data, 'C')
        nG <- str_count(temp_data, 'G')
        
        # GC content
        GC_content[i] <- (nC+nG) / len
        
        # CpG rate
        CpG_rate[i] <- nCpG/len
    }
    result <- list(GC_content=GC_content, CpG_rate=CpG_rate, n_divData=n_divData)
    return(result)
}

# Assign CpG rates (according to GC content) to specified lists 
div_by_range <- function(result){
    GC_content <- result$GC_content
    CpG_rate <- result$CpG_rate
    n_divData <- result$n_divData
    
    
    GCgt_h <- list() 
    for (i in 1:n_divData){
      # if (i%%10000 == 0){print(i)}
      
      # (0.8, 1]
      if (GC_content[i] > 0.8){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.8']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.8']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # (0.75, 0.8]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.8 & GC_content[i] > 0.75){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.75']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.75']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # (0.7, 75]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.75 & GC_content[i] > 0.7){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.7']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.7']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # (0.65, 0.7]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.7 & GC_content[i] > 0.65){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.65']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.65']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # (0.6, 0.65]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.65 & GC_content[i] > 0.6){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.6']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.6']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # (0.5, 0.6]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.6 & GC_content[i] > 0.5){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0.5']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0.5']], CpG_rate[i])}
      # [0, 0.5]
      else if (GC_content[i] <= 0.5){
        GCgt_h[['GCgt0']] <- c(GCgt_h[['GCgt0']], CpG_rate[i])}
    }
    
    return(GCgt_h)
}

# Visualise as histograms
viz_GCgt_h <- function(GCgt_h){
    par(mfrow=c(3,3), mar=c(3,3,1,1))
    for (key in names(GCgt_h)){
      hist(GCgt_h[[key]], breaks = 20, main = key, xlab = 'CpG rate', 
           xlim = range(0, 0.25))}
    # textplot('x-axis: CpG rate', halign = "center")
}


# GC content plot
viz_GCcontent <- function(GC_content){
  GCplot_start <- 1
  GCplot_end <- 230
  GCplot_lim <- 920 # 230*4
  
  par(mfrow=c(4,1), mar=c(4,3,1,1))
  while(GCplot_end <= GCplot_lim){
    x <- seq((GCplot_start*len),(GCplot_end*len),256)
    plot(x, GC_content[GCplot_start:GCplot_end], 
         xlab='')
    GCplot_start <- GCplot_end + 1
    GCplot_end <- GCplot_start+229
  }
}

# Execute
exe_dat_exp <- function(dat){
  div_data <- divide_data(dat)
  result <- Count_CG(div_data)
  save(result, file = 'result.Rdata')
  GCgt_h <- div_by_range(result)
  save(GCgt_h, file = 'GCgt_h.Rdata')
  viz_GCgt_h(GCgt_h)
  # load('result.Rdata')
  viz_GCcontent(result$GC_content)
}

HMM pseudocodes: 1. HMM Forward algorithm

# Forward Algorithm
alphaforward_hmm <- function(N=4, len_T=10){
    forward <- matrix(0, N, len_T)
    a <- matrix(1/4, 4, 4)
    b <- 1/4
    pi <- rep(1/4, 4)
    
    # 1. initialization
    for (s in 1:N){
      forward[s,1] <- pi[s]*b
      # forward[s,1] <- pi[s]*b[s, 1]
    }
    
    # 2. Recursion
    for (t in 2:len_T){
      for (s in 1:N){
        forward[s, t] <- sum(forward[, (t-1)]*a[, s]*b)
        # forward[s, t] <- sum(forward[, (t-1)]*a[, s]*b[s, t])
      }
    }
    
    # 3. Termination
    forwardprob <- sum(forward[, len_T])
    
    result <- list('forward'=forward, 'forwardprob'=forwardprob)
    return(result)
}

  1. HMM Viterbi algorithm
viterbi_hmm <- function(N=4, len_T=10){
    viterbi <- matrix(0, N, len_T)
    backpointer <- matrix(0, N, len_T)
    a <- matrix(1/4, 4, 4)
    b <- 1/4
    pi <- rep(1/4, 4)
    
    # 1. Initialisation
    for (s in 1:N){
      # viterbi[s, 1] <- pi[s]*b[s, 1]
      viterbi[s, 1] <- pi[s]*b
      backpointer[s, 1] <- 0
    }
    
    # 2. Recursion
    for (t in 2:len_T){
      for (s in 1:N){
        # viterbi[s, t] <- max(viterbi[,(t-1)]*a[, s]*b[s, t])
        viterbi[s, t] <- max(viterbi[,(t-1)]*a[, s]*b)
        # backpointer[s, t] <- max.row(viterbi[, (t-1)]*a[, s]*b[s, t]
        backpointer[s, t] <- max.col(t(viterbi[, (t-1)]*a[, s]*b))
        print(viterbi[, (t-1)]*a[, s]*b)
      }
    }
 
    # 3. Termination
    bestpathprob <- max(viterbi[, len_T])
    print(t(viterbi[, len_T]))
    bestpathpointer <- max.col(t(viterbi[, len_T]))
    
    bestpath <- rep(0, len_T)
    bestpath[len_T] <- bestpathpointer
    for (t in rev(1:(len_T-1))){
      bestpath_row <- bestpath[(t+1)]
      bestpath[t] <- backpointer[bestpath_row, t+1]
    }
    
    result <- list('bestpath'=bestpath, 'bestpathprob'=bestpathprob)
    return(result)
}

  1. HMM Backward algorithm
betabackward_hmm <- function(N, len_T){
  betabackward <- matrix(0, N, len_T)
  
  # 1. initialization
  for (i in 1:N){
    betabackward[i,len_T] <- 1
  }
  
  # 2. Recursion
  for (t in 1:(len_T-1)){
    for (s in 1:N){
      betabackward[s, t] <- sum(t(a[s, ])*b[, (t+1)]*betabackward[, (t+1)])
    }
  }
  
  # 3. Termination
  backwardprob <- sum(t(pi)*b[, 1]*betabackward[, 1])
  
  return(backwardprob)
}
  1. HMM Forward-Backward algorithm
foward_backward <- function(len_T, V, Q, O){
  
  # initialise A and B
  a <- A
  b <- B
  
  xi <- list()
   
  # iterate until convergence
  while (residual > 10^(-5)){
    for (t in 1:len_T){
      for (j in 1:N){
        gamma[j, t] <- alpha[j, t]*beta[j, t]/forwardprob
        for (i in 1:N){
          xi[[str(t)]][i, j] <- (alpha[i, t]*a[i, j]*b[j, (t+1)]*beta[j, (t+1)])
                            /forwardprob
          }
        }
    }
    
    # M-step
    for (i in 1:N){
      for (j in 1:N){
        sumt_xi <- 0
        sumk_xi <- 0
        for (t in 1:(len_T-1)){
          sumt_xi <- sumt_xi + xi[str(t)][i, j]
          for (k in 1:N){sumk_xi <- sumk_xi + xi[[str(t)]][i, k]}
        }
        a[i, j] <- sumt_xi/ sumk_xi
      }
    }
    
    for (j in 1:N){  
      for (k in 1:N){
        sum_gamma <- 0
        for (t in 1:(len_T-1)){
          if (V[k]==O[t]){sum_gamma <- sum_gamma + gamma[j, t]}}
        b[j, k] <- sum_gamma / sum(gamma[j, ])
      }
    }
    
  }
  
}

q <- quantile(file$obsExp)
for (i in 2:5){
  acfname <- paste('acf_q', as.character(i), sep = '_')
  quant_file <- file[file$obsExp > q[i-1] & file$obsExp<q[i],]
  quant_file <- acf(quant_file$CpGcount, lag = 1000)
  assign(acfname, quant_file$acf)
}
